VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT html\.EscapeString|template\.HTMLEscapeString|bluemonday\.\w+
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:html\.EscapeString|template\.HTMLEscapeString|bluemonday\.\w+ && MISSING:test|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the presence of Go-specific XSS mitigation helpers such as html.EscapeString, template.HTMLEscapeString, or bluemonday sanitization.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Mitigation Identified: XSS.
